Anna Wilson-Jones https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Wilson-Jones 0 Anna Wilson-Jones (born in Woking, Surrey) is an English actress. She is probably best known for her roles as Juliet Miller in Hotel Babylon and main character Tim Bisley's ex-girlfriend Sarah in Spaced.
